<br>
I've always managed to get around the blindness part with our summoned gear and at level 51, I still wear a Coldstone in my range slot.<br>
<br>
Now I'm focussing on better resist gear and HPs I can't help but thinking that I'm wasting a slot just so I can see in the dark.<br>
<br>
Any other blind mages out there? Erudite's have the same problem, so what items do you use to see in the dark?<br>
<br>
Canelin.<br>
